ts Victor Magtanggol, the one who must eventually learn to use Mj\u00f6lnir to protect the world and his loved ones from M\u00f3\u00f0i, Thor's son and Magni's brother, who is upset for not inheriting Mj\u00f6lnir, and [[Loki]] who plans to spread chaos in the mortal world.<ref name=victorabout>{{cite web|URL=http://www.gmanetwork.com/entertainment/tv/victor_magtanggol/about/ |title=Victor Magtanggol |accessdate=July 16, 2018 |language=Filipino}}</ref>\n\n==Cast and characters==\n{{multiple image\n|direction = vertical\n|align = right\n|image1 = Alden Richards at the OMG Awards.jpg\n|caption1 = Alden Richards portrays Victor Magtanggol.\n|width1 = 150\n|image2 = Janine Gutierrez 2016.png\n|caption2 = Janine Gutierrez portrays Gwen Regalado.\n|width2 = 150\n|image3 = John Estrada.jpg\n|caption3 = John Estrada portrays Loki.\n|width3 = 150\n|image4 = Ortaleza.png\n|caption4 = Chynna Ortaleza portrays Lynette Magtanggol-Domingo.\n|width4 = 150\n|image5 = Benjie Paras NBA Asia Challenge 2010.jpg\n|caption5 = Benjie Paras portrays Erwin Bravo.\n|width5 = 150\n}}\n\n<!--Official cast billing from GMA Network-->\n;Lead cast\n* [[Alden Richards]] as Victor \"Hammerman\" Magtanggol<ref name=pepvictor>{{cite web|author1=PEP Troika |title=Victor Magtanggol ni Alden Richards, handa nang banggain ang Probinsyano ni Coco Martin|url=https://www.pep.ph/pepalerts/pep-troika/22315/victor-magtanggol-ni-alden-richards-handa-nang-banggain-ang-probinsyano-ni-coco-martin |accessdate=July 23, 2018 |work=PEP |publisher=Philippine Entertainment Portal, Inc. |date=July 23, 2018 |language=Tagalog, English}}</ref>\n* [[Coney Reyes]]<ref name=\"Cast\"/> as Vivienne Delos Santos-Magtanggol\n* [[Eric Quizon]]<ref name=\"Cast\"/> as Hector Regalado\n* [[Andrea Torres]]<ref name=\"Cast\"/> as [[Sif]] / Ms. S\n* [[Janine Gutierrez]]<ref name=\"Cast\"/> as Gwen Regalado-Corona\n* [[Pancho Magno]]<ref name=\"Cast\"/> as [[M\u00f3\u00f0i and Magni|M\u00f3\u00f0i]]\n* [[John Estrada]]<ref name=\"cast\">{