ue)|Stan Walters]]\n| con1 = Jack Paul\n| pen1 = Jack Paul\n| try2 = [[Karl Ifwersen]] 2\n| con2 = [[Karl Ifwersen]]\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Devonport Domain\n| attendance =\n| referee = J Herrick\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 10 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = City\n| score = 10-3\n| report = <ref name=\"grafton_beats_north_shore\" />| away = Otahuhu\n| try1 = J Sutton, [[Jim Rukutai]]\n| con1 = [[Ernie Asher]] 2\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Eustace\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 1\n| attendance = 2500\n| referee = T Hill\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 10 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 38-5\n| report = <ref name=\"grafton_beats_north_shore\" />| away = Newton\n| try1 = Cadman 3, [[Thomas McClymont]] 2, D Norgrove, W Walsh, L Martin, S Jones, [[Sam Lowrie]]\n| con1 = [[Thomas McClymont]] 2, J Winters 2\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Thomas\n| con2 = unknown\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 2\n| attendance = 2500\n| referee = [[Stan Weston]]\n}}\n \n===Round 5===\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 17 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Grafton\n| score = 14-10\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Grafton Beats City\n| page =8\n| work = New Zealand Herald |volume=LIII |issue=16259\n| date = 1916-06-19\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19160619.2.122.2\n| accessdate = 2019-08-14}}</ref>| away = City\n| try1 = [[Dougie McGregor]], [[Karl Ifwersen]] 2, Tait\n| con1 = [[Karl Ifwersen]]\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = J Sutton, V Barchard\n| con2 =\n| pen2 = [[Ernie Asher]] 2\n| stadium = Victoria Park 1\n| attendance = 3000\n| referee = T Fielding\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 17 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 35-6\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =North Shore V Newton\n| page =8\n| work = New Zealand Herald |volume=LIII |issue=16259\n| date = 1916-06-19\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19160619.2.122.2\n| accessdate = 2019-08-14}}</ref>| away = Newton\n| try1 = Perrett 2, [[Stan Walters (rugby league)|Stan Walters]], Nicholson, Colson, T Paul 2\n| con1 = Jack Paul 7\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = [[George Iles]], Tunamako\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 2\n| attendance = 3000\n| referee = F Tyson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 17 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Otahuhu\n| score = 5-5\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Otahuhu V Ponsonby\n| page =8\n| work = New Zealand Herald |volume=LIII |issue=16259\n| date = 1916-06-19\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19160619.2.122.2\n| accessdate = 2019-08-14}}</ref>| away = Ponsonby\n| try1 = Fisher\n| con1 =\n| pen1 = B Farrelly\n| try2 = D Norgrove\n| con2 =\n| pen2 = [[Charles Webb (rugby league)|Charles Webb]] (one mark)\n| stadium = Otahuhu\n| attendance =\n| referee = A Ferguson\n}}\n\n===Round 6===\nThe point scoring phenomenon [[Karl Ifwersen]] was missing for Grafton and possibly as a result Newton pulled off a massive upset when they defeated Grafton by 8 points to 3. Newton had conceded 73 points and scored just 11 over their previous two matches.\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 24 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Newton\n| score = 8-3\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Newton Defeats Grafton\n| page =8\n| work = New Zealand Herald |volume=LIII |issue=16265\n| date = 1916-06-26\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19160626.2.108.2\n| accessdate = 2019-08-10}}</ref>| away = Grafton\n| try1 = [[George Iles]], [[Bill Williams (rugby league)|Bill Williams]]\n| con1 = R Clark\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Ballantyne\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 3\n| attendance =\n| referee = F Thompson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 24 June\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 30-0\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =North Shore\u2019s Easy Win\n| page =8\n| work = New Zealand Herald |volume=LIII |issue=16265\n| date = 1916-06-26\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19160626.2.108.2\n| access